Package com.mlt.desktop.graphic

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Composition
    A composition concatenates a list of drawings with fill or draw operations.
    Drawing
    A basic drawing that packs the shape, the stroke, the fill and draw paints, and the hints to be applied.
    Hint
    A rendering hint key-value pair useful to save/restore hints during rendering operations.
    Render
    A render manages a list of drawings that have to be saved, restored or rendered in a given order.
